      • writeReport

        public boolean writeReport​(java.lang.String filename,
                           int[] rpts,
                           boolean batch_mode)
        Generates an HTML document with all the requested report information.
        Parameters:
        filename - the String file name
        rpts - the int[] denoting the desired reports to generate. The values must correspond to the enumerated types provided by this class.
        batch_mode - the boolean model batch mode indicator. If a model is writing a report in batch mode, any previous reports will be overwritten.
        Returns:
        the export status of the report

      • writeReport

        public boolean writeReport​(java.lang.String filename,
                           int[] rpts,
                           boolean batch_mode,
                           ProgressMon progress)
        Generates an HTML document with all the requested report information.
        Parameters:
        filename - the String file name
        rpts - the int[] denoting the desired reports to generate. The values must correspond to the enumerated types provided by this class.
        batch_mode - the boolean model batch mode indicator. If a model is writing a report in batch mode, any previous reports will be overwritten.
        progress - the ProgressMon used to capture the status of the report export.
        Returns:
        the export status of the report
